We don't want to be overly obsessed.

01:00:49.397 --> 01:00:50.314
We just wanna make sure

01:00:50.398 --> 01:00:52.649
we're having balanced
day in and day out meals,

01:00:52.732 --> 01:00:54.527
and then, you know,
you have some fun with it.

01:00:54.610 --> 01:00:56.404
Food is supposed to be fun.
It's supposed to be tasty.

01:00:56.487 --> 01:01:00.533
[Producer] What do you have
for after-school snack?

01:01:00.616 --> 01:01:02.117
After-school snack? Um...

