01:01:25.391 --> 01:01:26.517
Like, "No."

01:01:26.601 --> 01:01:29.437
'Cause I don't really like
to try new foods that much.

01:01:29.520 --> 01:01:30.812
And he's like, "Come on. Just try it."

01:01:30.896 --> 01:01:32.398
I'm like... [reluctantly] "Fine."

01:01:33.399 --> 01:01:35.108
And then I bit into it.

01:01:35.193 --> 01:01:37.486
I ran to the other end of the kitchen.

