Making sure you're getting
some good whole grains at breakfast

01:02:31.206 --> 01:02:32.874
and some fruit is a good goal there.

01:02:32.958 --> 01:02:36.044
Water... morning, noon,
and night is also...

01:02:36.127 --> 01:02:37.505
If you just did one thing

01:02:37.588 --> 01:02:39.005
and make sure your kids are drinking water

01:02:39.089 --> 01:02:41.925
