01:02:55.398 --> 01:02:56.940
<i>in all the things we're looking for.</i>

01:02:57.023 --> 01:02:59.985
<i>Fruit and vegetable consumption,</i>
<i>whole grain consumption goes up.</i>

01:03:00.068 --> 01:03:01.820
<i>Sodium and calorie consumption goes down.</i>

01:03:01.903 --> 01:03:03.863
<i>But also behavior.</i>

01:03:03.947 --> 01:03:06.074
So having family meals
and cooking is, like,

01:03:06.157 --> 01:03:07.410
one of the best things you can do.

